sentences.sentence: Heart-shaped cookie cutters come in many sizes.

sentences.sentence: Hu was born into a family of paper cutters.

sentences.sentence: In autumn the wood-cutters always came and felled some of the largest trees.
sentences.translation: 在秋天，伐木工人照例来砍伐一些最大的树。
